question: How many films did Hal Roach produce?
wikidata_query: PREFIX wdt: <http://www.wikidata.org/prop/direct/> PREFIX wd: <http://www.wikidata.org/entity/> SELECT (COUNT(?uri) as ?c) WHERE { ?uri wdt:P162 wd:Q72792 . }

question: List all boardgames by GMT.
dbpedia_query: PREFIX dbo: <http://dbpedia.org/ontology/> PREFIX res: <http://dbpedia.org/resource/> PREFIX rdfs: <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#> SELECT ?uri WHERE { ?uri dbo:publisher res:GMT_Games }
wikidata_query: PREFIX wdt: <http://www.wikidata.org/prop/direct/> PREFIX wd: <http://www.wikidata.org/entity/> SELECT ?uri WHERE { ?uri wdt:P31 wd:Q131436 . }

question: Which organizations were founded in 1950?
dbpedia_query: PREFIX dbo: <http://dbpedia.org/ontology/> PREFIX dbp: <http://dbpedia.org/property/> PREFIX rdf: <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#> SELECT DISTINCT ?uri WHERE { ?uri rdf:type dbo:Organisation { ?uri dbo:formationYear ?date } UNION { ?uri dbo:foundingYear ?date } UNION { ?uri dbp:foundation ?date } UNION { ?uri dbp:formation ?date } FILTER regex(?date, "^1950") }
wikidata_query: PREFIX wdt: <http://www.wikidata.org/prop/direct/> PREFIX wd: <http://www.wikidata.org/entity/> SELECT DISTINCT ?uri WHERE { ?type wdt:P279* wd:Q43229 . ?uri wdt:P31 ?type . ?uri wdt:P571 ?foundedAt . FILTER CONTAINS(STR(?foundedAt), "1950") }

question: Which state of the United States of America has the highest density?
dbpedia_query: PREFIX yago: <http://dbpedia.org/class/yago/> PREFIX rdfs: <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#> PREFIX dbp: <http://dbpedia.org/property/> PREFIX rdf: <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#> SELECT ?uri WHERE { ?uri dbp:densityrank ?density } ORDER BY ASC(?density) LIMIT 1
wikidata_query: PREFIX wdt: <http://www.wikidata.org/prop/direct/> PREFIX wd: <http://www.wikidata.org/entity/> SELECT DISTINCT ?uri WHERE { ?uri wdt:P31 wd:Q35657 ; wdt:P2046 ?area ; wdt:P1082 ?population . BIND((?population/?area) AS ?density) . } ORDER BY DESC(?density) LIMIT 1
